gimme_an_adjective
  1. If you do this:                                                      

     "/areas/Misc/Bad/c/Objects/generic_randomizer"->gimme_an_adjective();   
     "/areas/Misc/Bad/c/Objects/generic_randomizer"->gimme_an_adjective(0);  

     it will return an adjective who's first letter is a consonant.       

  1. If you do this:                                                      

     "/areas/Misc/Bad/c/Objects/generic_randomizer"->gimme_an_adjective(1);  

     it will return an adjective who's first letter is a vowel.           

